# Generate Access Review Report

## Configuration

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **Review Frequency** | {{ rbac_review_frequency }} |
| **Monitoring Warehouse** | `{{ rbac_monitoring_warehouse | upper }}` |
{%- if rbac_audit_scope == 'Specific Data Products' %}
| **Scope** | Specific Data Products |
| **Target Prefixes** | {{ rbac_target_prefixes | join(', ') }} |
{%- else %}
| **Scope** | Full Account |
{%- endif %}

## Report Sections

| # | Section | Health Check |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 1 | Executive Summary | User counts, bypass totals |
| 2 | ACCOUNTADMIN Holders | Match against authorized list |
| 3 | RBAC Bypasses | Direct user grants (expect: **0**) |
| 4 | Role Hierarchy Health | Depth violations (expect: all HEALTHY) |
| 5 | Dormant Users | Inactive 90+ days with roles |
| 6 | Recent Privilege Changes | Last {{ rbac_review_frequency | lower }} period |
| 7 | PUBLIC Role Grants | Should be minimal |
| 8 | MFA Status | Privileged users without MFA |

## Review Cadence

{%- if rbac_review_frequency == 'Weekly' %}
Run this report **every week**. Review lookback period: **7 days**.
{%- elif rbac_review_frequency == 'Monthly' %}
Run this report **every month**. Review lookback period: **30 days**.
{%- else %}
Run this report **every quarter**. Review lookback period: **90 days**.
{%- endif %}

## Action Items Template

After each review, complete these actions:

- [ ] Verify ACCOUNTADMIN holders match authorized list (Section 2)
- [ ] Remediate any RBAC bypasses found (Section 3)
- [ ] Fix role hierarchy depth issues (Section 4)
- [ ] Disable or remove dormant user access (Section 5)
- [ ] Review and approve recent privilege changes (Section 6)
- [ ] Revoke unauthorized PUBLIC grants (Section 7)
- [ ] Enable MFA for flagged users (Section 8)

